{"tid":1202454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］國歌法本月26或恢復二讀辯論！","createTime":"2019-06-11T09:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T09:18:22.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d7ae1cfa95b6b048180be33ec5c111b257c90f","tid":1202454,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"破例share熱狗<br />\n<br />\n聶德權去信內會　預告國歌法本月26日恢復二讀<br />\n<br />\n當《逃犯條例》二讀辯論仍未開始之際，另一極具爭議的《國歌條例草案》，亦即將於月底恢復二讀。 政制及內地事務局局長聶德權去信內會主席李慧琼，就他擬作出預告，將於6月26日恢復《國歌條例草案》二讀辯論。 就國歌法提出修正案作出的預告限期，為本月17日。 <br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-11-2019/53556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-11-2019%2F53556&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAowzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=89c4c4c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-11-2019/53556</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"560b7af3cb58afabde69b85506270dbb3fd95927","tid":1202454,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b8cc1b70e6ce90bf2c2a7b513b226a51827abd","tid":1202454,"uid":17222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1035263196500611/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsocrec%2Fvideos%2F1035263196500611%2F&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAowzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=9fa8f55f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1035263196500611/</a><br />\n咁多位巴打 可以既話阻你哋2分鐘<br />\n諗清楚自己出黎做咩 唔好因爲驚 你嘅一舉一動都可以帶動到其他人<br />\n祝你地今晚成功<br />\n曾經係前線的人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967144f4e0c79218b5beb0197051ad4eec08b296","tid":1202454,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:18:22.000Z"